lyrics:
[verse]
In a sunny island breeze, we gather around
With our chips and ice-cream, we're ready to astound
Crunchy and sweet, a unique combo we've found
Together they blend, the perfect harmony we've crowned

[chorus]
Oh, we're vibin' to the rhythm, feelin' so cool
Chips and ice-cream, breakin' all the rules
Floatin' on the reggae groove, taking it slow
Chips and ice-cream, oh, let the good vibes flow
